  ¬∑ suffices dual A K I * I ‚â§ dual A K 1 by
      convert mul_right_mono I‚Åª¬π this using 1; simp only [mul_inv_cancel hI, mul_one, mul_assoc]
    rw [‚Üê le_dual_iff A K hI]
